Text:
THANK YOU to team zwt and the uploader

Better instructions:

0) Check md5sum of keygen.exe
1) Install normally
2) Run keygen.exe *AS ADMINISTRATOR*
2a) Type in name and company as desired
2b) Press "Patch", select files and let the patch proceed
3) Run the application
4) When prompted, click to enter license data
5) When asked for the text of the license letter, enter nothing and proceed
6) Click button to enter license manually, follow instructions and enter data from the keygen window
